posting_body: ['-- Town Centre --', 'show contact info', 'Monthly Rent:', '$2000', 'Apartment:', '3 Bedroom | 2 Bathroom', 'Square Footage:', '1231 sq ft', "When you rent at Town Centre Apartment Homes, you have easy access to shopping, community events, and Eagan's many attractions.", 'Whether you like the energy of the city, or you prefer to spend your time on the many lakes and rivers in this area, you can do it all from Eagan, MN.', 'Visit Fort Snelling State Park or explore the Mississippi River.', 'Our apartments are also near major employers, the famous Mall of America, the Minneapolis-St. Paul International Airport, and all the amenities the Twin Cities have to offer.', 'Other nearby cities include Bloomington, Woodbury, Mendota Heights, and Minnetonka, MN.', 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $250.00, Rent $30.00, Deposit $250.00.', 'Breed Restrictions Apply.', 'Check out our beautiful community featuring:', '❖ Cardio Machines', '❖ Disposal Chutes', '❖ Elevator', '❖ Free Weights', '❖ Picnic Area', '❖ Playground', '❖ Pool', '❖ Recycling', '❖ Smoke-Free', '❖ Walking Trails', '❖ Barbecue/Grill Area', '❖ Controlled Access Building', '❖ Intercom/Call Box', '❖ Laundry Facilities/Laundry Room', '❖ Off-Street Parking', '❖ On-site Maintenance', '❖ On-site Management', '❖ Planned Social Activities', '❖ Video Surveillance', '❖ Yoga Studio/Room', 'Apartment features include:', '❖ Ceiling Fans', '❖ Dining Room', '❖ Dishwasher', '❖ Intercom/Call Box', '❖ Linen Closet', '❖ Microwave', '❖ Patio/Balcony', '❖ Views', '❖ Walk-In Closets In Select Homes', '❖ Wood Burning Fireplace In Select Homes (3rd Floor Only)', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Website:', '<URL>', '3475 Golfview Dr', 'Eagan, MN 55123', 'Lease Terms:', 'Variable', 'Managed by Weidner Apartment Homes, LLC', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'E930FCC8D8944A33']
